{"TopicId":163034,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"Trunk/paylod problem","CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T17:50:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T17:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have built this trunk but I cant seem to remove an object after it is placed unless I zoom in really close. Anyone have any common experiences or advice to fix it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002235631127822_a0d30cdca2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4289/35631127822_a0d30cdca2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002235800842975_29d21309af.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4260/35800842975_29d21309af.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T20:20:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do your colliders look like in Unity?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T21:01:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002235671403521_1b855fc635.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4240/35671403521_1b855fc635.jpg\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T21:36:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223115182\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499547661\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022harrisjosh2711\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, harrisjosh2711 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4240/35671403521_1b855fc635.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002235671403521_1b855fc635.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4240/35671403521_1b855fc635.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis that 4 convex collider segments that combine to create a cube shaped gap in the middle?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T22:57:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223115205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499549807\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105588\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CobaltWolf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, CobaltWolf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis that 4 convex collider segments that combine to create a cube shaped gap in the middle?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s kinda what it looks like. Honestly, It was such a rudimentary shape I didn\u0027t think I would need to create\u00A0a collider\u00A0in blender, I used unity\u0027s convex mesh. I have the time right this moment, I\u0027m going to make one in blender right quick and see if that fixes my issue\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T23:14:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223115205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499549807\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105588\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CobaltWolf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, CobaltWolf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis that 4 convex collider segments that combine to create a cube shaped gap in the middle?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m trying to use this collider now\u00A0but still having the same issue. Thanks for the help, I really appreciate it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002234995507173_12b4675c64.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4277/34995507173_12b4675c64.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bottle Rocketeer 500","CreatedById":178766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T23:18:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIDK how to do this, but if you can make it \u0022split\u0022 like the fairings do when you hover the mouse over them, it\u0027d be much easier to take stuff out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T23:23:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems that if my camera is below the bottom of the trunk\u00A0I cant select anything inside it without selecting it all as one piece. But if my camera passes the bottom of the trunk\u00A0I can select it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002235805700155_37f3f25061.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4213/35805700155_37f3f25061.jpg\u0022\u003E\u00A0Cant select\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002235805717545_21bf2f8bfb.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/35805717545_21bf2f8bfb.jpg\u0022\u003E\u00A0Can select\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-08T23:40:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223115281\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499556234\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022harrisjosh2711\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, harrisjosh2711 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems that if my camera is below the bottom of the trunk\u00A0I cant select anything inside it without selecting it all as one piece. But if my camera passes the bottom of the trunk\u00A0I can select it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou need to split the collider into segments - how can you use the interior if the physics see it at one convex mesh! The colliders need to, roughly, actually reflect the shape you\u0027re trying to achieve. See this screenshot - a roughly trapezoid shape collider that I then duplicate around. I then made different ones for each side of the \u0027wedge\u0027 cutout, and a squat cylindrical one to fill out the bottom of the part.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022YuXYYGX.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YuXYYGX.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QZ0rnlV.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QZ0rnlV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"harrisjosh2711","CreatedById":177745,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-09T02:35:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGot you! makes perfect sense. Thanks again!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: Split the colliders and it works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-09T03:36:57Z\u0022 title=\u002207/09/2017 03:36  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by harrisjosh2711\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}